<br>
8 total people were involved. 3-60 Epic Wizzies, 2-60 Enchanters, 57 Cleric, 58 Paladin, and 58 Ranger.<br>
<br>
We formed up and bound at the Fear portal, buffed up including SoW and Invis and all zoned in together. Invis held so we ran down to WW camp spot. We grouped up tight together then everyone dropped invis and we let the mobs come at us. We mezzed the first 3 or 4 then had the paladin and ranger run north and south to agro more mobs. The enchanters then started the Stunweb as mobs came in.<br>
Once we had 10 or 12 mobs we started AoE bombing them. The 3 wizzies moved out away from the group and turned back to face the enchanters. We formed a rough triangle and all pushed the mobs into the center with Thunderclap spells. Then we stepped in and started chaining Jylls. A short time later all the mobs were dead. <br>
<br>
The groups took about very little damage. Then we sat meditated and started to pull north. We cleared the entire western half of the zone in 3 pulls. Then we cleared the Amys in the temple and killed the Shissar for one of our Enchanters Epics.<br>
<br>
We had a great time and with an experienced AoE group it was very EZ to accomplish.<br>
<br>
Aumadar &lt;the mad bomber&gt; Arkanum <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufaerwyndcorpserunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Faerwynd Corpserunner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/31/02 1:07:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12207.topic&index=23>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Questions</span><hr size=1> I have tried 2 ways that work well, and Ill share both.<br>
<br>
The first takes a 3 groups, a melee group, an ae group, and a back up ae group.<br>
<br>
1- send in melee group uninvis, and have them head directly to west wall- their enchanter mezzing what he can when he gets there.<br>
<br>
2- AE group 1(with 2 56+ wizards minimum) follows them in 20 seconds after first group starts to zone and hits the mobs from behind<br>
<br>
3- AE group 2(mages, druids etc) zones in 15 seconds after the first group, runs to west wall and starts to ae.<br>
<br>
4- everyone else zones in 10 seconds increments and joins the fun.<br>
<br>
Try to camp a cleric from one of the first 3 groups just in case, but you shouldnt wipe out. Also, have AE people and clerics bind outside the portal- they can do a quick mem, and run back in and do more dmg and possibly save the day.<br>
<br>
Second strategy-<br>
<br>
Requires a bard, or another soe rabit, and a CoH mage.<br>
<br>
1- Rabbit zones in uninvis, circles the portal twice to get aggro, and heads nw dragging everything with them.<br>
<br>
2- Rabbits group zones in about 10 seconds behind, moves slightly south behind portal, and heads to west wall.<br>
<br>
3- BEFORE the rabit dies- CoH them to the group- this erases their aggro.<br>
<br>
4- Meanwhile, other groups are zoning in 15 second intervals and heading to the camp.<br>
<br>
Done correctly, both should require no CR at all, other than the people that fall initially. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12207.topic&index=23><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=12207.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=12207.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12207.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12207.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm40">Off-Topic Funhouse<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value=